    "startTime": 480.72,
    "endTime": 483.68,
    "text": "the sketch that kept recurring this line"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.68,
    "endTime": 486.319,
    "text": "this street"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.319,
    "endTime": 488.4,
    "text": "the street that connects the band's past"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.4,
    "endTime": 490.16,
    "text": "with their present the tight rope that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.16,
    "endTime": 493.36,
    "text": "they walk as activists and artists a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493.36,
    "endTime": 495.52,
    "text": "walk through cinema that allows the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.52,
    "endTime": 497.84,
    "text": "bands to become protagonists"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.84,
    "endTime": 501.319,
    "text": "in their own poetry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.81,
    "endTime": 501.95,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.95,
    "endTime": 507.58,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.58,
    "endTime": 509.44,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.44,
    "endTime": 518.399,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.399,
    "endTime": 520.719,
    "text": "the end of the show is like the end of a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.719,
    "endTime": 522.8,
    "text": "flight it's an arrival"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.8,
    "endTime": 524.32,
    "text": "it's a transfer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.32,
    "endTime": 525.76,
    "text": "from the stage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.76,
    "endTime": 527.839,
    "text": "out to the audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.839,
    "endTime": 530.16,
    "text": "for the british band take that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.16,
    "endTime": 532.48,
    "text": "we ended the show by sending an 80 foot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.48,
    "endTime": 534.8,
    "text": "high mechanical human figure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.8,
    "endTime": 537.11,
    "text": "out to the center of the crowd"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.11,
    "endTime": 545.44,
    "text": "[Applause]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.44,
    "endTime": 548.0,
    "text": "like many translations from music to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.0,
    "endTime": 550.16,
    "text": "mechanics this one was initially deemed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.16,
    "endTime": 552.88,
    "text": "entirely technically impossible"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 552.88,
    "endTime": 555.12,
    "text": "the first three engineers we took it to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.12,
    "endTime": 556.32,
    "text": "said no"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.32,
    "endTime": 558.32,
    "text": "and eventually the way that it was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 558.32,
    "endTime": 560.08,
    "text": "achieved was by keeping the entire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.08,
    "endTime": 563.04,
    "text": "control system together while it toured"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.04,
    "endTime": 564.64,
    "text": "around the country so we had to fold it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.64,
    "endTime": 567.04,
    "text": "up onto a flatbed truck"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 567.04,
    "endTime": 568.8,
    "text": "so it could tour around without coming"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.8,
    "endTime": 570.399,
    "text": "apart and of course"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.399,
    "endTime": 572.16,
    "text": "what this meant was that the dimension"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.16,
    "endTime": 575.2,
    "text": "of its head was entirely determined by"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.2,
    "endTime": 577.92,
    "text": "the lowest motorway bridge that it had"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 577.92,
    "endTime": 580.0,
    "text": "to travel under on its tour and i have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.0,
    "endTime": 582.959,
    "text": "to tell you that it turns out there is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.959,
    "endTime": 585.839,
    "text": "an unavoidable and annoyingly low bridge"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.839,
    "endTime": 589.56,
    "text": "just outside hamburg"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.69,
    "endTime": 596.8,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.8,
    "endTime": 599.68,
    "text": "another of the most technically complex"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.68,
    "endTime": 601.76,
    "text": "pieces that we've worked on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.76,
    "endTime": 604.88,
    "text": "is the opera carmen at bregenz festival"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.88,
    "endTime": 607.12,
    "text": "in austria"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 607.12,
    "endTime": 610.24,
    "text": "we envisaged carmen's hands rising"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.24,
    "endTime": 612.08,
    "text": "out of lake constance and throwing this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612.08,
    "endTime": 613.68,
    "text": "deck of cards in the air and leaving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.68,
    "endTime": 615.12,
    "text": "them suspended"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.12,
    "endTime": 617.68,
    "text": "between sky and sea but this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.68,
    "endTime": 619.6,
    "text": "transient gesture this flick of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.6,
    "endTime": 620.72,
    "text": "wrists"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 620.72,
    "endTime": 622.48,
    "text": "had to become a structure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 622.48,
    "endTime": 624.24,
    "text": "that would be strong enough to withstand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.24,
    "endTime": 627.04,
    "text": "two austrian winters"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.04,
    "endTime": 628.56,
    "text": "so there's an awful lot that you don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.56,
    "endTime": 630.72,
    "text": "see in this photograph that's working"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.72,
    "endTime": 634.32,
    "text": "really hard it's a lot of ballast and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.32,
    "endTime": 636.0,
    "text": "structure and support around the back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.0,
    "endTime": 636.88,
    "text": "and i'm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.88,
    "endTime": 638.16,
    "text": "i'm going to show you the photos that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.16,
    "endTime": 639.92,
    "text": "aren't on my website"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.92,
    "endTime": 642.32,
    "text": "the photos of the back of the set the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.32,
    "endTime": 643.36,
    "text": "part"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.36,
    "endTime": 645.04,
    "text": "that's not designed for the audience to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.04,
    "endTime": 649.279,
    "text": "see however much work it's doing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.0,
    "endTime": 653.76,
    "text": "and you know this is actually the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.76,
    "endTime": 655.839,
    "text": "dilemma"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 655.839,
    "endTime": 657.76,
    "text": "for an artist who's working as a stage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.76,
    "endTime": 658.839,
    "text": "designer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.839,
    "endTime": 663.2,
    "text": "because so much of what i make is fake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.2,
    "endTime": 665.92,
    "text": "it's an illusion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.92,
    "endTime": 668.959,
    "text": "and yet every artist works in pursuit of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 668.959,
    "endTime": 671.839,
    "text": "communicating something that's true"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.839,
    "endTime": 675.04,
    "text": "but we are always asking ourselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.04,
    "endTime": 677.12,
    "text": "can we communicate truth using things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.12,
    "endTime": 679.68,
    "text": "that are false"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.16,
    "endTime": 682.079,
    "text": "and now when i attend the shows that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.079,
    "endTime": 683.519,
    "text": "i've worked on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.519,
    "endTime": 685.839,
    "text": "i often find i'm the only one who's not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.839,
    "endTime": 688.24,
    "text": "looking at the stage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.24,
    "endTime": 690.56,
    "text": "i'm looking at something that i find"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.56,
    "endTime": 693.519,
    "text": "equally as fascinating and it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.519,
    "endTime": 696.16,
    "text": "the audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.64,
    "endTime": 699.519,
    "text": "i mean where else do you witness this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 699.519,
    "endTime": 701.279,
    "text": "this many humans"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 701.279,
    "endTime": 703.36,
    "text": "connected focused"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.36,
    "endTime": 704.959,
    "text": "undistracted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 704.959,
    "endTime": 708.12,
    "text": "and unfragmented"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 708.399,
    "endTime": 710.079,
    "text": "and lately i've begun to make work that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710.079,
    "endTime": 712.399,
    "text": "originates here"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.399,
    "endTime": 716.399,
    "text": "in the collective voice of the audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.399,
    "endTime": 718.0,
    "text": "poem portraits"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.0,
    "endTime": 720.56,
    "text": "is a collective poem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.56,
    "endTime": 722.399,
    "text": "it began at the serpentine gallery in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 722.399,
    "endTime": 724.48,
    "text": "london and everybody"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.48,
    "endTime": 727.68,
    "text": "is invited to donate one word"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 727.68,
    "endTime": 729.76,
    "text": "to a collective poem and instead of that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729.76,
    "endTime": 732.48,
    "text": "large single led portrait that was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 732.48,
    "endTime": 734.24,
    "text": "broadcasting to the back of the stadium"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.24,
    "endTime": 735.519,
    "text": "in this case"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.519,
    "endTime": 737.279,
    "text": "every member of the audience gets to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.279,
    "endTime": 738.88,
    "text": "take their own portrait home with them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 738.88,
    "endTime": 740.959,
    "text": "and it's woven in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.959,
    "endTime": 742.88,
    "text": "with the words that they've contributed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 742.88,
    "endTime": 744.639,
    "text": "to the collective poem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 744.639,
    "endTime": 746.72,
    "text": "so they keep a fragment of an ever"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 746.72,
    "endTime": 749.68,
    "text": "evolving collective work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.68,
    "endTime": 751.68,
    "text": "and next year the collective poem will"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 751.68,
    "endTime": 755.04,
    "text": "take architectural form"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 755.519,
    "endTime": 758.72,
    "text": "this is the design for the uk pavilion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 758.72,
    "endTime": 762.399,
    "text": "at the world expo 2020"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 762.399,
    "endTime": 764.959,
    "text": "the uk"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 764.959,
    "endTime": 766.959,
    "text": "in my lifetime it's never felt this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 766.959,
    "endTime": 769.04,
    "text": "divided"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 769.04,
    "endTime": 771.2,
    "text": "it's never felt this noisy with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 771.2,
    "endTime": 773.04,
    "text": "divergent voices"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 773.04,
    "endTime": 775.36,
    "text": "and it's never felt this much in need of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 775.36,
    "endTime": 777.6,
    "text": "places where voices might connect and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 777.6,
    "endTime": 778.8,
    "text": "converge and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 778.8,
    "endTime": 780.8,
    "text": "it's my hope that this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 780.8,
    "endTime": 783.2,
    "text": "wooden sculpture this wooden instrument"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 783.2,
    "endTime": 785.04,
    "text": "a bit like that violin i used to play"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785.04,
    "endTime": 786.399,
    "text": "might"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 786.399,
    "endTime": 788.639,
    "text": "be a place where people can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 788.639,
    "endTime": 790.72,
    "text": "play and enter their word"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 790.72,
    "endTime": 793.2,
    "text": "at one end of the cone emerge at the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 793.2,
    "endTime": 795.279,
    "text": "other end of the building and find that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.279,
    "endTime": 797.68,
    "text": "their word has joined a collective poem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797.68,
    "endTime": 801.24,
    "text": "a collective voice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 805.9,
    "endTime": 809.88,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.0,
    "endTime": 815.2,
    "text": "these are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 815.2,
    "endTime": 818.639,
    "text": "simple experiments in machine learning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 818.639,
    "endTime": 820.399,
    "text": "the algorithm that generates the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820.399,
    "endTime": 823.12,
    "text": "collective poem is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 823.12,
    "endTime": 825.44,
    "text": "pretty simple it's it's like predictive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 825.44,
    "endTime": 827.519,
    "text": "text only it's trained"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 827.519,
    "endTime": 830.48,
    "text": "on millions of words written by poets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.48,
    "endTime": 832.72,
    "text": "in the 19th century so it's a sort of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.72,
    "endTime": 834.24,
    "text": "convergence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 834.24,
    "endTime": 836.639,
    "text": "of intelligence past and present"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 836.639,
    "endTime": 839.36,
    "text": "organic and inorganic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 839.36,
    "endTime": 840.8,
    "text": "and we were inspired by the words of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.8,
    "endTime": 842.639,
    "text": "stephen hawking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 842.639,
    "endTime": 844.16,
    "text": "towards the end of his life he asked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.16,
    "endTime": 846.32,
    "text": "quite a simple question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.32,
    "endTime": 849.199,
    "text": "if we as a species were ever to come"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.199,
    "endTime": 851.6,
    "text": "across another advanced"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 851.6,
    "endTime": 855.04,
    "text": "life form an advanced civilization"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 855.04,
    "endTime": 857.76,
    "text": "how would we speak to them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 857.76,
    "endTime": 860.48,
    "text": "what collective language would we speak"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 860.48,
    "endTime": 863.12,
    "text": "as a planet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 863.76,
    "endTime": 865.92,
    "text": "the language of lights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 865.92,
    "endTime": 868.32,
    "text": "reaches every audience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.32,
    "endTime": 869.92,
    "text": "all of us are touched by it none of us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 869.92,
    "endTime": 872.32,
    "text": "can hold it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 872.32,
    "endTime": 874.639,
    "text": "and in the theater we begin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 874.639,
    "endTime": 877.12,
    "text": "each work in a dark place devoid of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 877.12,
    "endTime": 879.68,
    "text": "light we stay up all night focusing the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 879.68,
    "endTime": 882.72,
    "text": "lights programming the lights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 882.72,
    "endTime": 884.639,
    "text": "trying to find new ways to sculpt and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 884.639,
    "endTime": 887.279,
    "text": "carve light"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 889.28,
    "endTime": 891.279,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 891.279,
    "endTime": 894.399,
    "text": "this is a portrait"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 894.48,
    "endTime": 897.199,
    "text": "of our practice"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 897.44,
    "endTime": 899.12,
    "text": "always seeking new ways to shape and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.12,
    "endTime": 901.519,
    "text": "reshape light"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 901.519,
    "endTime": 903.6,
    "text": "always finding words for things that we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 903.6,
    "endTime": 906.959,
    "text": "no longer need to say"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 908.48,
    "endTime": 910.32,
    "text": "and i want to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 910.32,
    "endTime": 913.12,
    "text": "say that this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 913.12,
    "endTime": 915.6,
    "text": "and everything that i've just shown you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 915.6,
    "endTime": 919.49,
    "text": "no longer exists in physical form"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 919.49,
    "endTime": 920.8,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 920.8,
    "endTime": 922.079,
    "text": "in fact most of what i've made over the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 922.079,
    "endTime": 925.12,
    "text": "last 25 years doesn't exist anymore"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 925.12,
    "endTime": 927.199,
    "text": "but our work endures in memories in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 927.199,
    "endTime": 929.76,
    "text": "synaptic sculptures"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 929.76,
    "endTime": 931.6,
    "text": "in the minds of those who were once"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 931.6,
    "endTime": 932.959,
    "text": "present"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 932.959,
